OL,3,CMurder investigation launched after
OL,4,Cman dies in hit-and-run
OL,6,FTwo people have been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of murder following a hit-
OL,8,Fand-run in Doncaster.
OL,10,FPolice were called at 8.32pm on Friday
OL,11,F10 April to reports of a road traffic
OL,12,Fcollision at Prince's Street in
OL,13,FDoncaster.
OL,15,FIt is reported that a silver Hyundai
OL,16,Fwas involved in a collision with a
OL,17,Fpedestrian and failed to stop at the
OL,18,Fscene.
OL,20,FThe pedestrian, a 26-year-old man,
OL,21,Fdied in hospital a short time later.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/2
